reviewText: My great- grandsons are enjoying the series now.

This dvd is only 10 episodes. You can get literally the entire series of this show for only a couple dollars more right here on Amazon. That's 30 more episodes, 4 times the content for just a couple extra bucks. Heck, some places you can find the complete series for the same price as this, sometimes LESS! (I've seen it for 5) but yeah. Do not buy this DVD. There's no reason for this DVD to even exist with how cheap you can currently get the complete series.
